{"tid":1590164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，中共之所以強大，係因為人皆有貪念，個個貪平買大陸嘢","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T15:57:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d07fc6914bbb955dfb23bbc915a5b427c2d1e634","tid":1590164,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"改革開放後，中共美其名讓一部分人富起來，其實就係以極權壓榨十幾億人，用平價賤賣佢哋嘅勞力換取外匯儲備，令中共印嘅人民幣愈嚟愈有影響力。<br />\n除咗造成多國大量嘅貿易逆差，亦令好多國際企業極度依賴中共嘅供應鏈，愈嚟愈泥足深陷，美國好多龍頭企業反貿易戰就係例子。<br />\n<br />\n所以，對外國宣傳中共惡行固之然重要，但發係一場全球性嘅排華，罷買共貨嘅行動更為有用。<br />\n<br />\n昨天它偷了你的貨幣，今天他偷了你的技術，明天他就偷了你的家園。"},{"pid":"d24a75426c6dd3fca3b76ae61bcade8a5daa557b","tid":1590164,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"b3d27f895d0471da22cd078a32c5bc0b620455ff","tid":1590164,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:16:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"184b088d37e8d4258842a23f652e7b31ff45746c","tid":1590164,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"支那野既質素<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}